Question:8
Create 5x6 an array and find the mean?
In [8]:
arr5 = np.random.randint(1,20, size = (5,6))
print("Original Array: \n")
print (arr5)
print("\n")
print("Mean of Array: \n")
print(arr5.mean())
Original Array: 

[[10 17  3  1 12 12]
 [ 9 11  4 16  7  6]
 [ 6 16 19  8 15 10]
 [ 9 10  4 16 11 16]
 [14 13 13 11  8 16]]


Mean of Array: 

10.766666666666667
