Question:12
Create a 4x4 an array and find the sum of diagonal elements?
In [12]:
arr = np.random.randint(1,20, size = (4,4))
print("Original Array: \n")
print (arr)
print("\n")
print("Sum of diagonal elements of Array: \n")
print(np.trace(arr))
Original Array: 

[[16 11 18 12]
 [11 16 10 16]
 [ 4  7 10 16]
 [17 14  7  7]]


Sum of diagonal elements of Array: 

49
Question:13
